{
  "stem": "1363.4",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "But, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] [SIGHS] I don't consider myself a nutcase, if you know what I mean.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Because there are, and I do understand, a lot of people who went through the concentration camps, who went through certain [SIGHS] hostilities, the same way as I did, that they became a bit paranoid with anything what has-- in connection with-- with Germans.",
      "word_count": 44
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 27,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They don't want to speak the language anymore, I know of people who went through much worse than I, and they don't want to talk about it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I don't.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I feel that we should.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It is our duty to let the world and the future know what has happened so it never, ever happens again.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can only tell everybody in the future, they should hang on, don't give up, because I could have given up many times.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "There were even small incidents in that year where they put me to the wall with a gun at me.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And I just hoped and hoped, and, and didn't think that everyone is as bad as certain people.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And I survived it.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, when this rape thing happened, and we got to the-- with the family-- oh, I didn't mention.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I got gonorrhea through that incident.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And I didn't have any medication.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "There was no medicine at all.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So, a month or two after, we got a Red Cross parcel from the Australian relations.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And in there was a medication for that little girl and the grandma, penicillin.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "But they survived it without the penicillin.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So the penicillin was used to me and cured me for my gonorrhea.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So that was OK.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "But, my auntie and I were traveling in the country.",
      "word_count": 10
    }
  ],
